At the moment, it is easy to add help descriptions to existing help sections. However, with more and more macros getting added, it would be good to be able to create custom help categories to reduce the clutter in some sections (eg 'Advanced'). Particularly with plugins like Scaffolding, which have about a dozen macros of their own and can get lost in the current help section. If would be good to be able to create a new section ('Scaffolding' for example) in which my macros can describe themselves.

